@Version("1.2.0")

Package com.adobe.cq.wcm.core.components.models.datalayer.builder

This packages defines a helper utility for building data layer models for integration with Adobe Client Data Layer. All models can be built from DataLayerBuilder.

    DataLayerSupplier
    Data layer field value supplier.
